These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea, lemonade
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking lemonade##7
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Beverage   | tea | iced-tea | lemonade | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, goat, chinchilla
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the dog##7
3. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the chinchilla##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Pet   | dog | chinchilla | goat | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different games are played: go, snooker, billiard, chess
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing chess is somewhere between the person playing billiard and the person playing snooker##7
3. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | go | snooker | chess | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bolivar, alhambra, dannemann
1. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
2. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
3. the dunhill-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | alhambra | dunhill | dannemann | bolivar |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, spinach, strawberry, blueberry
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating spinach is between the person eating cherry and the person eating blueberry##2
3. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
4. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the person eating strawberry and the person eating blueberry##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Food   | strawberry | cherry | spinach | blueberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, april, may
1. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in january##7
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in may##7
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Birthday   | may | april | november | january |

